    "summary": "The user engages the assistant in a sociolinguistic discussion regarding the perceived competence of Standard English versus African American Vernacular English (AAVE) in academic settings. The assistant avoids reinforcing biases and instead identifies them, explaining how linguistic gatekeeping and unconscious bias serve to privilege dominant groups and marginalize minority identities.",
